description: The Russell 2000 Net TR aims to reflect the performance of the following market: US small and mid-cap stocks The 2000 smallest companies out of the 3000 largest companies in the US Weighted by free-float adjusted market capitalisation Semi-annual index review Additional information on the index, selection and weighting methodology is available at https://www.ftse.com
